# STREAMING::GET_USED_CREATOR_BUDGET

## Returns
* **FLOAT**

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
0.0 = no memory used
1.0 = all memory used

Maximum model memory (as defined in common\data\missioncreatordata.meta) is 100 MiB
